    "content": "Beyonce - Sweet Dreams\r\n\r\nBassline is pretty much this throughout. It's aceee.\r\n\r\nTabbed By : SamLawd\r\n\r\nTuning:Standard\r\n                             \r\n[tab]G|------------------------------15-13-11-10-------------------------------13h15-13-11-10-|\r\nD|----13-13h15p13-11-11--8~-9~-----------------13-13h15p13-11-11-------------------------|\r\nA|----------------------------------------------------------------9~-11~-----------------|\r\nE|-11---------------------------------------11-------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nListen out for the timings and when to play it, it stops at verses.\r\n\r\nSorry it's all on one line. It's still pretty a pretty ace bass line.",
